title: Unlocking the Draft Vault with Daniel Jeremiah
itunes:title: Unlocking the Draft Vault with Daniel Jeremiah
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news in the NFL including Derek Carr's big extension, more Kyler Murray drama looming, and AJ Green staying with the Cardinals. The busiest man alive in the month of April, draft guru Daniel Jeremiah, joins the show to UNLOCK THE VAULT of the Draft.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
